title: I don't know what skin rito gave me for thr 10 year anniversary
body: I got the icon for the 10 year anniversary but i dont know what i got for the mystery skin since i have the riot kayle already. plz help

replies.body: The gifts are being sent out individually per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  You won't get everything all at once, so hang tight until everything is wrapped out and sent to the many eligible accounts.  Patience!
